headline: Cordless Power Tools Market Research Report 2025-2030 | IoT Integration and Sustainable Materials Fuel Innovations
summary: The global Cordless Power Tools Market was valued at USD 25 million in 2024 and projected to reach USD 37.20 million by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.85%. Key advancements include smart features like integrated Bluetooth and smartphone connectivity for tool tracking. The U.S.-China trade war impacts costs and availability. Industry 4.0 technologies enable mass customization, while vendors focus on sustainability with recycled materials. Segments like drilling & fastening and sawing & cutting lead
